Here are some tutorial sites that features picture uploading that might be worth while in Meteor:
This one seems like it will work well with the iron router
https://medium.com/@victorleungtw/how-to-upload-files-with-meteor-js-7b8e811510fa#.9n0xjyy6d
It is based on:
https://github.com/CollectionFS/Meteor-CollectionFS



Another package:
https://github.com/tomitrescak/meteor-uploads


External API:
https://meteor.hackpad.com/Meteor-Cookbook-Filepicker.io-Uploads-and-Image-Conversion-hIpSwJQV3HJ

And a good tutorial:
http://experimentsinmeteor.com/page2/

